These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: epic, musical
City: hannover, nizza
1. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | epic  | musical |
| City     | nizza | hannover  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: eggplant, kiwi
2 different games are played: billiard, domino
1. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Food    | eggplant      | kiwi         |
| Game   | billiard | domino |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, soy-milk
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: february, august
1. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | milk   |
| Birthday       | august  | february |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-4::.
There 2 different types of food: onion, nectarine
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, parkour
