.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| Food   | onion  | nectarine |
| Sport         | cycling | parkour    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-5::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, ship
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, horror
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |   2    |
| Transport      | jet-ski | ship |
| Movie-Genre   | horror        | crime  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-6::.
